node.text:
To celebrate the launch of our brand new Cozy-Up 2-In-1 Bedside Sleeper & Bassinet we teamed up with our friend Natalie from @babysleeptrainer to help you learn some tips and tricks for those first few days, weeks and months with your baby! ❤️💤

Pssst! We're going live with Natalie on Tuesday! Leave a question @babysleeptrainer in the comments below. 👇
